info.description:
Sale Tax Included
=================

Adiczion's Tryton Module: sale_tax_included
-------------------------------------------

Adds the ability to Tryton to make sales and invoices with product with 
price with tax included.

.. warning::
   Replace the deprecated module : sale_b2bc.

Installing
----------

See INSTALL
